sher=蘋果日報 |date=2014-03-28 |accessdate=2014-04-21 |archive-date=2016-04-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160404030701/http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20140328/368635/?fb_comment_id=fbc_488248254634008_2506042_488275071297993#f15f273bf476224 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

===中興大樓盥洗室使用爭議===
